<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Smirch" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Smirch,</orth> to smear, to daub, to soil: <bibl n="shak. ado 3.3.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 3, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ado 4.1.135" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 135</bibl> (Ff <emph>smeared</emph>). <bibl n="shak. ayl 1.3.114" default="NO" valid="yes">As I, 3, 114</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 3.3.17" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 III, 3, 17</bibl>. cf. <emph>Besmirch, Unsmirched.</emph>
